{"tid":330810,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"依家當紅果幾個差唔多同期既偶像實力派聲優...你會點排","createTime":"2017-07-21T14:36:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T07:17:15.000Z","uid":6327,"like":4,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"7485f77245a4c22e6f299ccc96535a7a6a327e0b","tid":330810,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T14:36:18.000Z","msg":"講緊係佐倉綾音 茅野愛衣 東山奈央 早見沙織<br />\n<br />\n論聲音辨識度就佐倉=早見&gt;東山&gt;愛衣<br />\n唱功就東山&gt;其餘三個<br />\n身材應該得佐倉同愛衣爭下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n配音實力佐倉應該最勁 太多奇怪聲線同感情轉換<br />\n娛樂性就一定係東山...個樣表面蠢萌實際精過鬼<br />\n(近期爆笑演出係超時空三角個演唱會跳舞)<br />\n<br />\n呢四個代表角色都比較多而且叫做係配音行先<br />\n一諗起聲優就諗到角色：佐倉就一色  愛衣就白<br />\n東山就千刺(+各類疑似援交) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n早見就雪乃呢個第三者<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n某d聲優配都未配得掂就搞一大堆個人fans活動又成日自拍乜乜柒柒 冇人記得你配過d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7e03131e0d872c2941a6838430fc89e6da2f8dc","tid":330810,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T14:38:01.000Z","msg":"井式中文<br />\n正皮"},{"pid":"5f29906d116d28633de70b73470125705515e157","tid":330810,"uid":6327,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T14:38:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>井式中文<br />\n正皮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認真post黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97d91f0e954aba7a723b7478930dbdf161250a65","tid":330810,"uid":35556,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T14:40:08.000Z","msg":"論演技係佐倉最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你係太高估佐倉定低估東山同早見"},{"pid":"2bad2f3260c9d0c386639db42f39708cc73f3bd1","tid":330810,"uid":41849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T14:40:26.000Z","msg":"Naonao 英語擔當<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74d9666c1bbdfbe760e55ddf105eb619646c863a","tid":330810,"uid":34293,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T14:42:04.000Z","msg":"水瀨祈fuck the world"},{"pid":"6b1cb5b18ba4a12338ffbc65e99ae0256f78fba5","tid":330810,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T14:44:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>論演技係佐倉最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你係太高估佐倉定低估東山同早見</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個人意見姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我抽呢四個出黎 都係算係同期最top果幾個<br />\n咁我覺得佐倉比較略勝一籌 <br />\n青春少女型既角色我諗佐倉淨係會輸比香菜<br />\n<br />\n早見唔知係咪因為聲線所限 <br />\n有時想配d搞笑角色會好奇怪 唔係話佢差<br />\n東山都唔差既  <br />\n閣下有個別意見 不妨詳談<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d69e6bd377a1a5f92f4e2df4fd8bca9494bf562","tid":330810,"uid":6327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T14:46:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>水瀨祈fuck the world</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n強化版小倉唯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be107f309a2a5ddb7233e1e129bfc9b0e116f623","tid":330810,"uid":46389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T14:46:28.000Z","msg":"話戲路佐倉最闊我同意，但講演技一定早見行先"},{"pid":"6d1051bf73fc8c9079671d21bcdb583aeb4e7c43","tid":330810,"uid":30745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T14:46:41.000Z","msg":"冇臭菜嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4dc0a2be2e89fce6e20609546fe81bdecfd9e61","tid":330810,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T14:47:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>水瀨祈fuck the world</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n強化版小倉唯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小瀨祈唱歌已經係jpop一線級"},{"pid":"a089dc16657d3f3d1f2daeea843c84e6457b735d","tid":330810,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T14:47:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話戲路佐倉最闊我同意，但講演技一定早見行先</blockquote><br />\n狂賭g淵"},{"pid":"5bae81a641ce47aaf7c0f20b2076ef07062b5d42","tid":330810,"uid":30745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T14:48:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>水瀨祈fuck the world</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n強化版小倉唯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小瀨祈唱歌已經係jpop一線級</blockquote><br />\n佢唱歌真心好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n戰姬果時已經覺得好撚神"},{"pid":"fd091a534649f47452dc443d8e73a39ef008b10c","tid":330810,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T14:49:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇臭菜嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔算同期啦 呢四個係英超水平<br />\n香菜係西超"},{"pid":"7518eaf7263df33f845c6c1e6c9898e0393092fa","tid":330810,"uid":35556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T14:50:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>論演技係佐倉最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你係太高估佐倉定低估東山同早見</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個人意見姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我抽呢四個出黎 都係算係同期最top果幾個<br />\n咁我覺得佐倉比較略勝一籌 <br />\n青春少女型既角色我諗佐倉淨係會輸比香菜<br />\n<br />\n早見唔知係咪因為聲線所限 <br />\n有時想配d搞笑角色會好奇怪 唔係話佢差<br />\n東山都唔差既  <br />\n閣下有個別意見 不妨詳談<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果計演技既話<br />\n早見&gt;東山&gt;&gt;&gt;佐倉&gt;茅野<br />\n聲線變化<br />\n東山&gt;早見&gt;=佐倉&gt;茅野"},{"pid":"ac1af016d4574f2473a098609bd713f5845f6556","tid":330810,"uid":55375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T14:51:05.000Z","msg":"講樣早見嬴哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee873519e32eafdae6f76b78c9212073cb5dfc20","tid":330810,"uid":6327,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-