lyTime":"2017-07-21T15:00:26.000Z","msg":"我覺得平野綾尾機<br />\n不過好似唔同期"},{"pid":"71e7b967a72723886078a7c5c2d7d79695247bcc","tid":330810,"uid":6327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T15:01:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>話戲路佐倉最闊我同意，但講演技一定早見行先</blockquote><br />\n狂賭g淵</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講起狂賭 一開始我都好期待早見會有咩突破性演出<br />\n咁的確都有些少咁既突破既<br />\n但其實都好平凡 高潮暴走<br />\n愛衣係初戀怪獸已經展示左一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第一次接觸早見係只有神知道的世界(好似係<br />\n不過biliibili又無得比我重溫<br />\n我都幾中意佢，姐姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n早見呢排聽多左 <br />\n依家都係想睇佢把咁soft既聲配d鳩野"},{"pid":"35248a5ce6650b6a98999b5958f295944e05256d","tid":330810,"uid":122997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T15:01:34.000Z","msg":"如果佳村遙肯train吓的唱功同台風,好大幾會彈得起(前題係比人私有化之前)<br />\n樓主,你當中二病二人組死?"},{"pid":"4b2e2d17c2b4078e051bd356032d9ef6ff353c94","tid":330810,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T15:02:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雨宮天</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n閣下覺得雨宮天會勁過以上邊一個？"},{"pid":"867786530dc7beb915c4cefd8132d56b57b58244","tid":330810,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T15:02:37.000Z","msg":"阿澄佳奈亞子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94cd17f97e108e8beda65a8d26760f8cf9ab103e","tid":330810,"uid":19837,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T15:03:22.000Z","msg":"佐倉把聲太好認<br />\n反而愛衣可以配到好大反差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時真係聽唔出"},{"pid":"05367f55790efc116f23e939c403ea1e31682b22","tid":330810,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T15:05:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果佳村遙肯train吓的唱功同台風,好大幾會彈得起(前題係比人私有化之前)<br />\n樓主,你當中二病二人組死?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得一個聲優比人記入腦始終要靠配音行先既<br />\n配音六成 唱四成 <br />\n <br />\n中二病二人組乜水？"},{"pid":"ea7aa768d3b606089f6b9dde065aaee673f1181a","tid":330810,"uid":100412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T15:06:27.000Z","msg":"四個入面唔使睇CAST表都認得把聲嘅淨係得早見同茅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ebdffc1e83a1df1fd12578b8e69fbf2994ed736","tid":330810,"uid":3342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T15:06:33.000Z","msg":"種田梨沙"},{"pid":"5e92021de748aa1df8b1fba5a3dcfd03b07d97eb","tid":330810,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T15:07:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得平野綾尾機<br />\n不過好似唔同期</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n進修完好似勁左"},{"pid":"3247391e56c407946daf2671ae9ad4dc18eabcbf","tid":330810,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T15:09:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佐倉把聲太好認<br />\n反而愛衣可以配到好大反差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時真係聽唔出</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一開始我都以為佐倉紅得起係靠其他野<br />\n但睇左好多聲優延伸既video睇佢地平時把聲同配音把聲 睇完真係覺得佐倉好屈機<br />\n<br />\n愛衣真係幼至幾歲老至阿嬸都配到<br />\n甚至癲喪角色 可以睇下初戀怪獸唔知第幾集"},{"pid":"3cb711ebe10be10944a77a17b5a73975b6eaa339","tid":330810,"uid":46389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T15:10:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>種田梨沙</blockquote><br />\n傳頌之物遊戲版把聲毒性超高"},{"pid":"2a42c18ff84c7430c34f25c3c5890908cc893e6b","tid":330810,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T15:10:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>四個入面唔使睇CAST表都認得把聲嘅淨係得早見同茅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最易認就一定係早見 能登二號機黎"},{"pid":"3a48946acfd01f7e567f23bab2887f22d356ec66","tid":330810,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T15:11:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>種田梨沙</blockquote><br />\n盾妹一早已變成李依的形狀了"},{"pid":"31f